high_descs: Walk around the counter to the back side of the knife.
Pick up the knife from the counter that is behind the sink.
Turn right, walk past the pot, through the living room, and through the bedroom door on the left up to the foot of the bed.
Place the knife into the pot that is on the bed.
Pick up the pot with the knife inside of it from the bed.
Walk around the bed to the sidetable against the wall.
Place the pot with the knife inside of it on top of the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Store a Knife and Pot on the SideTable.

high_descs: Turn left. When you reach the end of the knife, turn right. Turn right, move and then turn right.
Grab the knife.
Turn right. At the end of the cabinet, turn left. Reach the wall. Turn left. Reach the pot.
Place the knife on the pot.
Grab the two-handled pot and the knife.
Turn right. At the end of the bed, turn left. Reach the sidetable.
Place the pot and knife on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Search for a knife. Find a pot with two handles. Place them on a side table.

high_descs: Walk to the other side of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Turn right and head left to walk into the bedroom on the left.
Put the knife in the pot on the bed.
Pick up the pot from the bed.
Turn right to reach the side table.
Put the pot on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Put the pot with the knife on the side table.
